CASE HAVING BEEN FINALLY HEARD ON 03.01.2019, THE COURT ON THE SAME DAY PASSED THE FOLLOWING: OB a Crl.MC.No. 8707 of 2018 2011KERMAL 2 ORDER Learned counsel appearing for the petitioner seeks permission to withdraw this petition with liberty to challenge the order framing charge by the court, if he is otherwise entitled to do so. Permission granted. Accordingly this Crl.M.C is dismissed as withdrawn reserving liberty with the petitioner to challenge the order framing charge by the court, if he is otherwise entitled to do so.
